strings:
<voice_0x01001C69><se_high>Princess Medea: I've been thinking a lot about Prince Charmless<endash> ...I mean, Charmles.
He isn't anything like I imagined.
<voice_0x01001C6A><se_high>Princess Medea: What am I going to do?
<voice_0x01001C6B><se_high>Princess Medea: I must respect my grandmother's wishes.
<voice_0x01001C6C><se_high>Princess Medea: But... Do you think people can change after they get married?

<voice_0x01001C6E><se_high>Princess Medea: I know, I know, <hero>.
I could also be quite self-centred when
I was younger.
<voice_0x01001C70><se_high>Princess Medea: Perhaps Prince Charmles will grow out of it, too...
